<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1038600" n="172r"/>
    <opener><lb/>Viro Illustrissimo ac Doctissimo <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119166895"><abbr>P. A.</abbr> Michelotti</rs>
        <lb/><abbr>S. P. D.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-102552517"><abbr>Nic. B.</abbr></rs></opener>
<p><lb/>Grata mihi fuit omnino gratulatio Tua facta ob matrimonium,
                              <lb/>quod haud pridem contraxi, pro qua gratulatione Tibi debitas refe<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ro gratias cum voto omnigen<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> prosperitatis, quam Tibi<del> finem</del> porro
                              <lb/>animitus apprecor. Nova rei familiaris cura, studiumque
                              <lb/>Juris quod magis excolere debeo <choice><orig><g ref="#klammerauf">|:</g></orig><reg>(</reg></choice>nuper enim factus sum
    <lb/>Assessor <rs type="organisation">Facultatis Juridic<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs><choice><orig><g ref="#klammerzu">:|</g></orig><reg>)</reg></choice> ali<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> caus<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> re<subst><del>rum</del><add>bus</add></subst> mathe<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>matic<subst><del>arum studio</del><add>is</add></subst> <add>me</add> fere avocant, dabo tamen operam, ne
                              <lb/>opus, quod aliquando edendum promisi, frustra expectes.</p>
    <p><lb/>Gaudeo quod sub finem <date when="1720-08">hujus mensis</date> doctissim<subst><del>am</del><add><choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></add></subst> Tu<subst><del>am</del><add><choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></add></subst> <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_M3G2JA79">disser<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tation<subst><del>em</del><add>is</add></subst></rs> editionem absolutum iri spem facias; sed mihi valde
        <lb/>displicet, quod in <rs type="letter" key="B_991170515150605501">litteris</rs> ad <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509969">Patruum</rs> meum nobis iterum adimas
                              <lb/>spem Te hic videndi; gratum certe mihi futurum fuisset,
                              <lb/>si in <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>dibus quas nuper emi hospitio <add>Te</add> excipere et aliquandiu
                              <lb/>retinere potuissem, oro autem ut, qu<subst><del>od</del><add>ia</add></subst> hoc anno <subst><del>fiere non</del><add>non</add></subst>
                              <lb/>potes, alio tempore nos nostrasque oras invisas.</p>
    <p><lb/><del>Proposui Patrua dubia </del>Accedo ad dubia, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> in <subst><del>t</del><add>T</add></subst>uis <rs type="letter" key="B_991170517025405501">litteris</rs>
                              <lb/><del>Acced </del>movisti. Ais Te jure dubitare num verum sit, quod in
        <lb/>a<choice><orig><g ref="#nn">n̄</g></orig><reg>nn</reg></choice>otationibus <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-117589144">Patruelis</rs><note type="internal">ToDo: Herausfinden, worum es sich bei den annotationibus von Joh. I B. handelt, eventuell in einem Joh. I B.-Michelotti-Brief. Es sind Anmerkungen, die vermutlich separat geschickt wurden. 1719-10-18 schreibt joh. I B. er werde sich mit dem Tentamen befassen, sobald er Zeit hat, die Annotationes wurden also nach diesem Datum geschrieben.</note> mei in <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_8VCJJVI7">Tentamen <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1055365613">Keilii</rs> de Motu Mus<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>culorum</rs> dicitur, Mercurium, qui cutem membranam crassam
                              <lb/>penetrat, non penetrare epidermidem membranam tenuissimam.
                              <lb/>Objicis exemplum inunctionis mercurialis, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> in Lue Venerea<note type="comment">Syphilis.</note>
                              <lb/>laborantibus peragitur, et in qua mercurius et epidermidem
                              <lb/>et cutem penetra<del>n</del>t. Respondetur brevibus: Aliud obtinere in
                              <pb facs="1038601" n="172v"/>
<lb/>cute animalis vivi, <subst><del>In</del><add>in</add></subst> qua pori sunt hiantes, aliud in cute vel
                              <lb/>pelle animalis mortui, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> poros habet constrictiones frigoreque
                              <lb/>consolidatos. Quod attinet ad alterum dubium circa vim inflationis
    <lb/>in vesiculis <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1055365613">Keillianis</rs>, ad id quidem etiam respondere volebam, sed quia
        <lb/>careo <add>et</add> <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_8VCJJVI7">libro</rs> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1055365613">Keillii</rs> <add>et a<choice><orig><g ref="#nn">n̄</g></orig><reg>nn</reg></choice>otationibus <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509969">Patrui</rs> in hunc <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_QV3XWE3G">librum</rs></add>, sensum qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stionis, licet verb<subst><del>is</del><add>a</add></subst> Tu<subst><del>is</del><add>a</add></subst> attente perlege<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rim, percipere non potui, credo autem ipsummet <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509969">Patruum</rs>, cui 
        <lb/><rs type="biblio" key="biblio_M3G2JA79">schedulam</rs> Tuam perlegendam tradidi, sufficienter Tibi responsu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rum esse. Dissertatio <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-120379260">Scheuchzeri</rs> de <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_BS83R2A4">usu Matheseos in Medicina</rs>
        <lb/>non amplius prostat, neque etiam hic invenitur <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-120597519">Groningii</rs> <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_D9K78QUC">Hi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>storia Cycloidis</rs>, posterior hic liber, ni fallor, <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-2911298">Hamburgi</rs> impres<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>sus est, et fortassis per Bibliopolam vestrum <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1037587715">Hertz</rs> facile
        <lb/>comparari poterit. <subst><del>Misi</del><add>Dedi</add></subst> nuper<del> per</del> <rs type="person">amic<subst><del>um</del><add>o</add></subst></rs> <subst><del>quon</del><add>cui</add></subst>dam, <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-3173435">Me<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>diolanum</rs> profecto <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_43V6EF8W">Dissertationes</rs> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-12209025X">Werenfelsii</rs> nostri, quem
    <lb/>librum iste amicus porro ad <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-117589144">Patruelem</rs> meum vel Bibliopolam
        <lb/><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1037587715">Hertz</rs> <rs type="place" key="place_VER-repven">Venetias</rs> mitti curabit, pretium ejus amicus ille, <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> quo
                              <lb/><del>librum </del>eundem hunc librum nitide compactum comparavi,
                              <lb/>mihi nondum significavit, credo autem esse 10<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice> Librarum
        <lb/>Vestratium.<note type="internal">ToDo: Währung</note> Salutem rogo ut dicas amicis co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>unibus, <abbr>D.<hi rend="sup">nis</hi></abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118901125">Smith</rs>,
    <lb/><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-117596027">Zendrin<subst><del>i</del><add>o</add></subst></rs>, ut et <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-117589144">Patrueli</rs> meo. Vale meque amiciti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
                              <lb/>porro co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>endatum habe. </p>
    <closer><dateline>Dabam <rs type="person" key="place_GEO-2661604">Basile<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> <date when="1720-08-10"><abbr>d.</abbr>
                                    <date when="1720-08-10">10. <abbr>Aug.</abbr> 1720</date>.</date></dateline></closer>
</div>
